\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid1732375 PAUL:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 
You thought it was a bonus }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\ul\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 because}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535  you got the idea of change coming in there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid1732375 W.M.:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 
Well, when I went there, that was the original idea, but, in fact, it faded fairly quickly, because, again, I suppose one is influenced by \'85 well, first of all, I\rquote 
d been influenced by Alwyn, who persuaded me that rural communities were relatively stable a
nd unchanging, with primary relationships as distinct from secondary relationships in the town, where you got a bus ticket from a conductor without knowing who he is, and so on.
