\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid2099945 W.M.:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 None at all \endash 
 apart from getting me in!  She was \'85 she actually stopped teaching in the school before I started the work.  Or did she stop just \'85 anyway, she wasn\rquote 
t teaching in the school very long afterwards, but it might have created problems.  But I was known as her husband, for quite a long time, and \'85
