\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid8588501 W.M.:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 
Which again, most people didn\rquote t seem to appreciate.  He said that he was friendly with a personal assistant to the Governor of Illinois, when he was in Chicago, and he was talking to the chap one day, and he said \'85
 the man said that the Governor trusted him implicitly.  And Cicourel said, \'93I can demonstrate to you that this man does not trust you implicitly, and I\rquote ll do it by doing nothing\'94.  So he bet him a hundred dollars \'85
 have you heard this story before?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid8588501 PAUL:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 No.
