\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid12279015 W.M.:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 Now they do
, yes.  But the assumption was, in those days, that people didn\rquote t read them, you know, because they weren\rquote t graduates, and you could be a little more secure in thinking that, but you certainly couldn\rquote 
t do it with an English village or wherever you are.  So \'85 and I didn\rquote t \'85 I didn\rquote t give anyone false names because it struck me that this was pointless, because people want to find out, and \'85
