No?  Where did they go?  May have been Kent, I can\rquote t remember.  But I do remember, there were two anthropologists \endash  husband and wife \endash  who were in Swansea, he was a lecturer, she was a researcher, both got jobs as anthropologists, in 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\ul\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535  Sociology Department somewhere, one of the newer Departments.
