\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f42\fs22\insrsid2717339\charrsid10757096 PAUL:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid2717339   \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f42\fs22\insrsid12849482\charrsid7821535 
We always have had some anthropologists, but that\rquote s always \'85 after the first little bit, of course.  Yes.  Well, that\rquote s very interesting.  And, at Swansea, who were your most important colleagues, you know, influential \'85
 on your life and so on?
